+7. [P2] Fix 5 footer CTA is still the old filled variant - `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:1304-1311` still uses `style={{backgroundColor: primaryColor}}`, has no `variant="outline"`, and lacks the helper row with `cart.cta.need_help_or_bill` plus inline `Bell`. FIX: switch the empty-cart table-tab footer to the locked outline layout and add the helper paragraph.
 
